{"tid":1975154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲大學生支持香港，卻面臨被開除學藉","createTime":"2020-04-16T10:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T16:33:58.000Z","uid":36073,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2c3934c24923879081e339ad668f98504daf00da","tid":1975154,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:47:21.000Z","msg":"澳洲昆士蘭大學學生會長 Drew Pavlou ，曾經在社交網站批評大學的親中共態度及支持香港抗爭運動，近日大學以紀律處分並會解除學藉。<br />\n<br />\n昆士蘭大學發言人確認 Pavlou 將被開除但拒絕回應原因，也說這次開除並非因他的鮮明政見，續指大學期望所有學生能夠遵守規則以反映價值觀與社會期望。<br />\n<br />\nPavlou 在大學多次抗議指出學校的研究經常跟擁有中國背景的機構合作；而在上年校園裡支持香港抗爭運動時被中國政府支持者襲擊；中國媒體也批評過 Pavlou 的反中立場。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立即簽名聯署！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/vXFFgzKmPp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FvXFFgzKmPp&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=1c16191b\" target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/vXFFgzKmPp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\nStudent who criticised China faces expulsion from University of Queensland<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theaustralian.com.au/higher-education/student-who-criticised-china-faces-expulsion-from-university-of-queensland/news-story/3305e48d89eeae3f7f4ca9758f68f46b?fbclid=IwAR2kz1TlRpXLmmfjurFow7ME9kHkRxKc_Uak0VohEOkD3hbyDS0NvuzEriw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fhigher-education%2Fstudent-who-criticised-china-faces-expulsion-from-university-of-queensland%2Fnews-story%2F3305e48d89eeae3f7f4ca9758f68f46b%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2kz1TlRpXLmmfjurFow7ME9kHkRxKc_Uak0VohEOkD3hbyDS0NvuzEriw&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10PzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=ec8c988b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theaustralian.com.au/higher-education/student-who-criticised-china-faces-expulsion-from-university-of-queensland/news-story/3305e48d89eeae3f7f4ca9758f68f46b?fbclid=IwAR2kz1TlRpXLmmfjurFow7ME9kHkRxKc_Uak0VohEOkD3hbyDS0NvuzEriw</a>"},{"pid":"b00a0b7eb8b94865c90a1d1087ea4180c3126d96","tid":1975154,"uid":200722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:48:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4abc64882c7faf4ca084e175b8c14a463a554db","tid":1975154,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"已簽<br />\n不過算啦<br />\n今時今日讀大學=dum錢落海"},{"pid":"258fc0db8026fe949e2917afb56f24bd24aa9669","tid":1975154,"uid":104502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T10:52:29.000Z","msg":"應該可以做司法覆核？"},{"pid":"8f9b79609e5052a58bf343f5cbaf6155641bb9f9","tid":1975154,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ea03505ddffabbf31802c8eb7995432fe499f2","tid":1975154,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"五毛唔識推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de3c85185c26edfa1b74c062fd9d3dc3ef18ee52","tid":1975154,"uid":223780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:10:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07dd65dff602615abd5601c9fbf1c69f801e5c68","tid":1975154,"uid":223664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"51f66196fbb672a7daad557915b5b07ffaf19ae5","tid":1975154,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:35:42.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eef7425ed4da10ef6015f6ff073fb1e10a0c30